The '''Leek''' is found via [[foraging]] in the [[Spring]], or grown from [[Spring Seeds]]. 

Leeks are most common on [[the Mountain]] and [[Backwoods]] maps, where 58% of spring forage items will be Leeks. They can also be found at the [[Bus Stop]] (20%), [[Railroad]] (20%) and the [[Farm Maps#Forest|Forest Farm]] (25%).

