==Tailoring==
Leek is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] with [[Cloth]] in the feed to create a {{name|Shirt042|link=Tailoring{{!}}Lime Green Tunic|class=inline}}. It is a white dye when used in the spool of the Sewing Machine with a dyeable clothing item in the feed.

==Quests==
*[[Evelyn]] requests a Leek by mail on the 15th of [[Spring]] (year 2) in the [[Quests#Granny's Gift|"Granny's Gift" quest]].  The reward is {{Price|500}} and 1 [[Friendship]] heart.
*A Leek may be randomly requested in [[Spring]] at the [[Quests#Help Wanted Quests|"Help Wanted" board]] outside [[Pierre's General Store]] for a reward of {{Price|180}} and 150 [[Friendship]] points.
*Evelyn requests 12 Leeks in the [[Quests#Gifts for George|"Gifts for George"]] Special Order. The rewards are {{Price|2000}} and a [[Coffee Maker]].

